Nutrient data for: CRUNCHY RICE & WHEAT FLAKES WITH APPLE CINNAMON CLUSTERS, UPC: 038000144844
Food Group:  Branded Food Products Database

RICE, WHOLE GRAIN WHEAT, SUGAR, WHEAT BRAN, ROLLED OATS, VEGETABLE OIL (HYDROGENATED COCONUT, SOYBEAN AND/OR COTTONSEED OIL, PALM KERNEL AND CANOLA OIL), CONTAINS 2% OR LESS OF SALT, SOLUBLE WHEAT FIBER, BROWN SUGAR SYRUP, NATURAL AND ARTIFICIAL FLAVOR, MALT FLAVOR, APPLES, DEXTROSE, WHEAT FLOUR, BROWN SUGAR (SUGAR, MOLASSES), CALCIUM CARBONATE, CINNAMON, SOY LECITHIN, HONEY, MOLASSES, BAKING SODA, MIXED TOCOPHEROLS FOR FRESHNESS, BHT FOR FRESHNESS. VITAMINS AND MINERALS: VITAMIN C (ASCORBIC ACID), REDUCED IRON, NIACINAMIDE, VITAMIN B6 (PYRIDOXINE HYDROCHLORIDE), VITAMIN B2 (RIBOFLAVIN), VITAMIN B1 (THIAMIN HYDROCHLORIDE), VITAMIN A PALMITATE, FOLIC ACID, VITAMIN B12, VITAMIN D3.
